      "text": "TROUBLE DIAGNOSIS"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Faulty Shifting"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Always perform the following preliminary checks before starting troubleshooting procedures when shift operation is faulty.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Note: The term \"faulty shifting\" indicates a significant variance from the shift characteristics.",
      "style": "note"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "flowchart",
      "title": "Faulty Shifting Diagnostic Flowchart",
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "n1",
          "type": "action",
          "text": "Check N-CVT fluid level"
        },
        {
          "id": "n2",
          "type": "terminal",
          "text": "Replenish N-CVT fluid (Check transmission main unit)"
        },
        {
          "id": "n3",
          "type": "action",
          "text": "Note: The transmission main unit may be damaged when shifting is faulty due to insufficient N-CVT fluid"
        },
        {
          "id": "n4",
          "type": "action",
          "text": "Check stall speed. Refer to \"Stall test\""
        },
        {
          "id": "n5",
          "type": "terminal",
          "text": "Check the electromagnetic clutch, N-CVT and brush holder"
        },
        {
          "id": "n6",
          "type": "action",
          "text": "Check throttle wire & throttle wire adjustment"
        },
        {
          "id": "n7",
          "type": "terminal",
          "text": "Adjust or replace the throttle wire"
        },
        {
          "id": "n8",
          "type": "action",
          "text": "Check control linkage"
        },
        {
          "id": "n9",
          "type": "terminal",
          "text": "Adjust control linkage"
        },
        {
          "id": "n10",
          "type": "action",
          "text": "Check shift characteristics"
        }
      ],
